README.md



     A curated list of awesome [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GIF]GIF
     resources

   Contents ·
   U
                                    se ·
   Authors ·
   License & Credits

   This is a list of tools, scripts, libraries, examples & other resources
   related to the Graphics Interchange Format (GIF) image format.

   [https://camo.githubusercontent.com/22f20c6e01284ec7147e2192580d188a5c9
   9c3f3/68747470733a2f2f64617669736f6e2e696f2f6173736574732f696d672f61776
   5736f6d652d6769662d6c6f676f2e676966]

