General Tools

     * [https://www.ffmpeg.org/]FFmpeg
     * [http://www.imagemagick.org/script/index.php]ImageMagick
     * [http://www.graphicsmagick.org/]GraphicsMagick - GraphicsMagick is
       usually faster than ImageMagick
     * [http://zulko.github.io/moviepy/]MoviePy - Python module for video
       editing

Utilities

     * [https://github.com/lukechilds/gifgen]Gifgen - Simple high quality
       GIF encoding
     * [https://github.com/vvo/gifify]Gifify - Convert any video file to
       an optimized animated GIF
     * [https://github.com/jclem/gifify]Gifify (not the same) - convert
       screen recording into GIF
     * [https://github.com/kornelski/giflossy]Gifsicle - lossy GIF
       compressor
     * [https://github.com/jglovier/gifs]Gifs - storage place for GIFs -
       [http://gifs.joelglovier.com/]demo
     * [https://github.com/yahoo/gifshot]Gifshot - create animated GIFs
       from media by Yahoo - [http://yahoo.github.io/gifshot/]demo
     * [https://github.com/videlalvaro/gifsockets]Gifsockets - Real Time
       communication library using Animated GIFs as a transport
     * [https://github.com/geelen/x-gif]X-gif - a web component for
       flexible GIF playback
     * [https://github.com/holman/gifme]gifme - generate animated GIFs
     * [https://github.com/yaronn/GifW00t]GifW00t - javascript web
       recorder
     * [https://github.com/lelandbatey/gif-machine]gif-machine - GIF
       creation from Youtube videos
     * [https://github.com/jbochi/gifstreaming]gifstreaming - Live video
       streaming server
     * [https://github.com/dergachev/screengif]Screengif - Create animated
       GIF screencasts
     * [https://github.com/sidorares/vnc-over-gif]vnc-over-gif - Serves
       screen updates as animated GIF over http
     * [https://github.com/jaipandya/gifdeck]gifdeck - Convert your
       SlideShares into animated GIFs
     * [https://github.com/schuyler/gifbot]Gifbot - GIF search for Slack
     * [https://github.com/FuzzyWobble/GIF-Camera]Gif-camera - create
       animated GIFs using webcam
     * [https://github.com/zehfernandes/gifline]Gifline - Chrome extension
       to put GIFs in your emails
     * [https://github.com/markjaquith/gifdrop]Gifdrop - Create a
       repository for your collection of gif images
     * [https://github.com/node-gh/gh-gif]Gh-gif - NodeGH plugin for
       commenting on pull requests/issues using GIF reactions
     * [https://github.com/z24/tty2gif]Tty2gif - record scripts and their
       outputs into both binary and GIF formats
     * [https://github.com/desktoppr/giftoppr]Giftoppr - Sync your
       favourite GIFs with Dropbox
     * [https://github.com/Fauntleroy/GIFit]Gifit - Chrome extension to
       make a GIF from a YouTube video
     * [https://github.com/spite/ccapture.js]Ccapture.js - Capture
       animations created with HTML5 canvas
     * [https://getkap.co/]Kap - Beautiful open-source app to capture your
       screen and export to GIF.
     * [https://github.com/rotblauer/gifit]Gifit (the other one) - Get a
       search resulting giphy GIF in markdown in stdout, ala $ gifit
       kittens.

Libraries

ActionScript

     * [https://github.com/theturtle32/Flash-Animated-GIF-Library]Flash
       Animated GIF Library - AS3 library for playing Animated GIFs in
